title: War of the Roses: The Cabin Alarm Kept Going Off
description: Laura is suspicious of her fiance Ben because the alarm at the family cabin kept going off.  Ben said he'd look into it but it was nothing.  After being at the cabin Laura noticed two major things that were off so now she's wondering if Ben is letting someone into the cabin and if that someone is a girl he's cheating on her with.
